{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-detail-js","path":"/post/how-to-auto-apply-coupon-code-in-magento-2/","result":{"data":{"wpPost":{"title":"How to Auto Apply Coupon Code in Magento 2","content":"\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magento\">Magento 2</a> is an extensively utilized e-commerce platform that offers a wide range of tools and functionalities to support merchants in developing their online store. Providing discounts and coupon codes to customers is a crucial factor in achieving success in online business as it can help increase sales and enhance customer satisfaction. Magento 2 offers the option to both <a href=\"/how-to-create-coupon-codes-in-magento-2/\">create coupon code in Magento 2</a> as well as auto-apply them, making it convenient for merchants to provide discounts to their customers in a hassle-free way.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our blog post aims to offer a comprehensive guide on <strong><em>how to auto apply coupon code in Magento 2</em></strong>, enabling merchants to provide discounts and promotional offers to their customers effortlessly. Automating this process can help merchants save valuable time while ensuring that the correct discounts are applied to each order, which can significantly impact driving sales and ultimately enhance the overall customer experience for online shoppers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Steps to Auto Apply Coupon Codes in Magento 2</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 1: Login to Magento 2 Backend</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To begin, log in to the Magento 2 backend using your admin credentials.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 2: Navigate to Promotions &gt; Cart Price Rules</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Go to the “Promotions” section, and then click on “Cart Price Rules”.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top\" cla